flowchart LR
    U[User / Judge] --> FE[Next.js Memory Debugger]
    FE --> API[FastAPI API]
    API --> COMP[Qwen structured compiler]
    COMP --> VAL[Schema + policy validator]
    VAL --> DB[(PostgreSQL hot index + audit)]
    SIM[Deterministic simulator] --> EVT[Event gateway]
    EVT --> ROUTE[Exact cue router]
    ROUTE --> DB
    ROUTE --> EVAL[Validity + inhibitor evaluator]
    EVAL --> QWEN[Qwen semantic adjudicator]
    EVAL --> POLICY[Policy gate]
    POLICY --> APPROVE[Human approval]
    APPROVE --> EXEC[Idempotent executor]
    EXEC --> DB
    WORKER[Absence + time worker] --> DB
    API --> OSS[Alibaba Cloud OSS]

